<tr><td>Infinite Energy</td><td>28995,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Energy = x</td><td>27472,x (x= 1-255)</td></tr>
</table>
<BR><BR><B>Change x to whatever value you wish, using the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI</B>
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>(Gerard Sweeney in Hack Attack III)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Type-in hacks</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD>This can be found in <a href="ftp://ftp.void.jump.org/pub/sinclair/magazines/YourSinclair/Issue40/Tape/">this issue of Pokes</a> in the alphabetical section.
 <i>(Cover Tape in Your Sinclair issue 40)</i> 

<br><hr>
Infinite lives:
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<pre>
 10 CLEAR 65535: LET t=0
 20 FOR f=65410 TO 65436
 30 READ a: POKE f,a
 40 LET t=t+(f- 65400)*a: NEXT f
 50 IF t<>72159 THEN STOP
 60 MERGE "": RUN USR 64510
 70 DATA 205,86,5,221,33
 80 DATA 0,64,17,120,191
 90 DATA&nbsp62,255,55,33,150
100 DATA 255,229,195,86,5
110 DATA 175,50,70,113,195
120 DATA 64,131
</pre>
 <i>(YS Smash Tips)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
